---
title: Cheesy Roasted Chicken with Green Peas and Roasted Potatoes
description: Tonight's roasted chicken is topped with white cheddar to make a perfect family night dinner! Our roasted potatoes and sweet peas will make even the most picky eaters warm up to this dish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-roti-au-fromage-573178e1.jpg
